"# Deploying the VPN Gateway

Follow these steps to configure the **site-to-site** tunnel. See the [vendor documentation](https://docs.example.com/vpn) for background.

## Prerequisites

| Item | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Public IP | 203.0.113.10 |
| Pre-shared key | stored in Passwords |

## Configuration

\`\`\`bash
config system ipsec
  set peer 203.0.113.10
  set psk-secret redacted
end
\`\`\`

-   Confirm firewall rules allow UDP 500/4500
-   Verify routing table includes the remote subnet
-   Test the tunnel with a ping across the link"
